OL,5,G0210 The Dog House
OL,6,     FRegal bassett hound Duchess is
OL,7,     Fback on the charm offensive.
OL,8,     FLoveable goofball Peaches puts
OL,9,     FJane and Alan in a spin. And
OL,10,     Fold-timer Hettie proves she's
OL,11,     Freally young at heart.
OL,12,G0305 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,13,     FIn Luton, there's unpalatable
OL,14,     Fbehaviour, curdled ice cream, an
OL,15,     Feggy mishap and a hair-raising
OL,16,     Fconfession, as three couples
OL,17,     Fcompete to host the best dinner
OL,18,     Fparty.
OL,19,G0400 Sunday Brunch
OL,20,     FSome extra brunch as Tim Lovejoy
OL,21,     Fand Simon Rimmer host the food and
OL,22,     Fchat show.
